snippet.title: Promessa - Gameplay
snippet.description:
This game was originally created for "Marcos Game Dev Jam 4" in 2 days, in this JAM the theme was "Shapeshifting"! Promessa came in 18th place standing out more in "Visual". :D

Play here:
